Merge pull request #10 from mawuli/patch-1

Add The Programming Language Zoo

Add The Programming Language Zoo

The Programming Language Zoo by Andrej Bauer is a collection of mini languages that demonstrate the design and implementation of programming languages using OCaml. Some of the languages in this grande Zoo include MiniML, MiniHaskell and Boa, an OOP language which combines features from Python and Javascript.
